---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Boat Propulsion System Design"
  description="Designed and integrated a propulsion system for an autonomous boat."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>Boat Propulsion System Design</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Designed and integrated a propulsion system to optimize performance
      within project constraints.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/images/projects/boat-propulsion.jpg"
      alt="Boat Propulsion System Design"
    />
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>

    <p>
      This project focused on selecting and integrating motors, batteries,
      shafts, and supporting components for an autonomous boat platform.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>

    <p>
      Component options were evaluated based on performance requirements,
      efficiency targets, budget constraints, and compatibility with the
      overall system architecture.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools Used</h2>

    <p>System Design • Analysis • Component Selection • Integration</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section + section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
</style>